lating%20the%20law%2C%20and%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Haryana%2C%20even%20suggested%20the%20failure%20to%20enforce%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolicy%20devised%20by%20you%26quot%3B%20to%20favour%20some%20farmers%20over%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20rapped%20the%20union%20government%20over%20%26quot%3Btoothless%26quot%3B%20environmental%20protection%20laws%2C%20observing%20that%20laws%20meant%20to%20control%20pollution%2C%20specifically%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%20Act%20of%202021%C2%A0had%20been%20passed%20sans%20the%20administrative%20machinery%20to%20ensure%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Section%2015%20of%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Act%20-%20which%20covers%20penalties%20for%20violating%20anti-pollution%20laws%20-%20had%20amended%20so%20%26quot%3Bprocedure%20for%20imposing%20penalty%20cannot%20be%20followed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2015%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20section%20for%20enforcing%20the%20EPA%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20was%20pointed%20out%2C%20to%20which%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20centre%2C%20said%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bfully%20operationalised%26quot%3B%20in%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNot%20A%20Single%20Prosecution...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20was%20the%20first%20to%20feel%20the%20court's%20wrath%2C%20with%20Justice%20Oka%20doubting%20its%20claim%20that%2044%20people%20had%20been%20prosecuted.%20%26quot%3BYour%20Advocate-General%20said%20nothing%20was%20done...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20told%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Punjab%20government%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20not%20a%20single%20prosecution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20told%20that%20Rs%2011%20lakh%20had%20been%20recovered%2C%20as%20fines%2C%20from%20417%20people%20violating%20the%20stubble%20burning%20laws%2C%20but%20declared%20itself%20unhappy%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bnominal%26quot%3B%20amounts%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgiving-you-1-week-supreme-court-rebukes-punjab-haryana-over-delhi-air-pollution-6800324%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPunjab%20Should%20Say%20It%20Is%20Helpless%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20On%20Delhi%20Air%20Pollution%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20impose%20nominal%20fines...%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Oka%20observed%20when%20told%20fines%20varied%20from%20Rs%202%2C500%20to%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20violator.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20given%20licence%20to%20people%20(to%20commit%20the%20crime)%20...%26quot%3B%20he%20noted%2C%20also%20asking%20Mr%20Singhvi%20why%20684%20others%20violating%20the%20same%20law%20had%20been%20spared%20any%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20government's%20Chief%20Secretary%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bvery%20small%20fires%26quot%3B%20were%20sometimes%20overlooked%2C%20to%20which%20the%20court%20responded%20sharply%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20minimum%20expected%20of%20you%20is%20to%20fine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaryana%20Govt%20'Under%20Fire'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20Haryana%20government%2C%20and%20lamented%20that%20not%20one%20prosecution%20had%20been%20recorded%20since%20June%202021%2C%20when%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%2C%20a%20central%20government%20panel%2C%20issued%20orders%20to%20prosecute%20those%20violating%20the%20anti-farm%20fires%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20claimed%20success%20in%20controlling%20farm%20fires%2C%20pointing%20to%20data%20that%20claims%20only%20655%20had%20been%20reported%20this%20year%20(of%20which%20around%20200%20were%20found%20to%20be%20false%20flags)%20compared%20to%20nearly%2010%2C000%20earlier%2C%20but%20the%20court%20was%20no