m%20campaigning%20for%20myself.%20I'm%20deeply%20grateful%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6A7JhOPB8C%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6A7JhOPB8C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Congress%20(%40INCIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1848991114935865451%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%2017%20when%20I%20campaigned%20for%20my%20father%20(former%20PM%20Rajiv%20Gandhi).%20Then%20I%20campaigned%20for%20my%20mother%20and%20brother%20and%20many%20of%20my%20colleagues.%20For%2035%20years%20I%20have%20been%20campaigning%20in%20different%20elections%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20I%20am%20campaigning%20in%20an%20election%20and%20seeking%20your%20support%20for%20myself.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20different%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20and%20thanked%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20for%20the%20opportunity%20to%20contest%20the%20election.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20my%20honour%20to%20represent%20you%20if%20you%20give%20me%20a%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said%20she%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20visited%20Mundakkai%20and%20Churalmala%20in%20Wayanad%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20devastating%20landslides%20that%20claimed%20over%20400%20lives%20and%20displaced%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20the%20devastation%20with%20my%20own%20eyes.%20I%20saw%20children%20who%20lost%20their%20families.%20I%20met%20mothers%20who%20lost%20their%20children.%20I%20met%20people%20whose%20entire%20life%20was%20washed%20away.%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20one%20thing%2C%20each%20and%20every%20person%20I%20met%20was%20engaged%20in%20helping%20each%20other.%20They%20supported%20each%20other%20with%20courage%2C%20without%20greed%20and%20with%20compassion.%20To%20be%20part%20of%20your%20community%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20great%20privilege%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%2