22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fzomato-increases-platform-fee-by-over-60-during-the-festive-season-read-the-companys-message-to-customers-on-the-fee-hike%2Farticleshow%2F114493578.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Landmark%20Verdict%2C%20Top%20Court%20Says%20States%20Can%20Rule%20On%20'Industrial%20Liquor'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20ruled%20that%20state%20governments%20can%20legislate%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20'industrial%20alcohol'%2C%20otherwise%20called%20'denatured%20spirits'%2C%20by%20including%20it%20under%20the%20term%20'intoxicating%20liquor'%20in%20the%20State%20List%2C%20i.e.%2C%20the%20list%20of%20subjects%20on%20which%20States%20can%20pass%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20members%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud-led%20nine-judge%20Constitution%20Bench%20found%20in%20favour%20of%20petitioning%20states%20-%20led%20by%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20including%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Kerala%20-%20while%20the%20ninth%2C%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%2C%20dissented.%20The%20majority%20ruled%20that%20the%20term%20'intoxicating%20liquor'%20cannot%20be%20understood%20to%20mean%20only%20that%20fit%20for%20human%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it%20will%20include%20all%20liquids%20that%20contain%20alcohol%2C%20even%20if%20not%20meant%20for%20human%20consumption%2C%20can%20be%20included%20in%20the%20term%20'intoxicating%20liquor'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20states'%20power%20to%20legislate%20could%20not%20be%20challenged%20since%20the%20law%20covers%20'intoxicating'%20and%20'industrial'%20products%2C%20and%20that%20the%20union%20could%20not%20take%20over%20this%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20ruling%20overturned%20a%2034-year%20decision%20by%20a%20seven-judge%20bench%20in%20Synthetics%20and%20Chemicals%20Pvt%20Ltd%20vs%20State%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20It%20was%20referred%20to%20a%20nine-judge%20bench%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20BV%20Nagarathna%2C%20however%2C%20ruled%20on%20the%20principle%20that%20'industrial%20alcohol'%20means%20it%20is%20not%20fit%20for%20human%20consumption%2C%20and%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20competence%20for%20the%20state%20legislature%26quot%3B.%20She%20said%20the%20decision%20in%20the%20Synthetics%20case%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bcorrectly%20decided%20by%20this%20court%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%20had%20been%20reserved%20in%20April%20after%20a%20marathon%20six-day%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20hearing%2C%20petitioners%20argued%20that%20if%20the%20power%20to%20regulate%20'industrial%20alcohol'%20goes%20to%20the%20centre%2C%20their%20hands%20would%20be%20tied%20when%20dealing%20with%20illegal%20consumption%20of%20'industrial%20alcohol'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna's%20dissenting%20opinion%20countered%20that%20argument%2C%20stating%20that%20just%20because%20'industrial%20alcohol'%20could%20be%20illegally%20consumed%20the%20State%20List%20could%20not%20be%20%26quot%3Bstretched%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%2C%20however%2C%20argued%20the%20power%20to%20regulate%20'industrial%20alcohol'%20had%20always%20been%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20judges%20on%20the%20bench%20were%20Justices%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%2C%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%2C%20JB%20Pardiwala%2C%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%2C%20Satish%20Chandra%20Sharma%2C%20and%20Augustine%20George%20Masih.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20asked%20to%20decide%20if%20the%20Industries%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Act%2C%20or%20the%20IRDA%2C%20of%201951%20allowed%20the%20union%20government%20to%20pass%20laws%20on%20the%20subject%20of%20'industrial%20alcohol'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20asked%20to%20rule%20on%20two%20key%20questions%3A%20a)%20should%20'industrial%20alcohol'%20be%20considered%20as%20'intoxicating%20alcohol'%20and%20therefore%20come%20under%20jurisdiction%20of%20States%2C%20and%20b)%20can%20state%20governments%20have%20control%20over%20'industrial%20alcohol'%20as%20it%20does%20with%20'intoxicating%20alcohol'%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20in%20question%20was%20Section%2018G%20of%20the%20IRDA%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20union%20government%20to%20ensure%20fair%20distribution%20and%20pricing%20of%20products%20from%20industries%20in%20scheduled%20lists%2C%20i.e.%2C%20from%20the%20list%20of%20subjects%20on%20which%20it%20is%20allowed%20to%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20was%20to%20Entry%2033%20of%20the%20third%20list%2C%20or%20the%20concurrent%20list%2C%20which%20gives%20state%20governments%20the%20power%20to%20regulate%20the%20trade%2C%20production%2C%20and%20distribution%20of%20'industrial%20alcohol'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20under%20Entry%208%20of%20the%20second%20list%2C%20States%20are%20empowered%20to%20regulate%20'intoxicating%20alcohol'%2C%20including%20production%2C%20possession%2C%20transport%2C%20purchase%2C%20and%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729664400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F6f5n98uo_supreme-court_625x300_03_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-industrial-liquor-verdict-in-landmark-verdict-top-court-says-states-can-rule-on-industrial-liquor-6853367%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20ruled%20that%20state%20governments%20can%20legislate%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20'industrial%20alcohol'%2C%20otherwise%20called%20'denatured%20spirits'%2C%20by%20including%20it%20under%20the%20term%20'intoxicating%20liquor'%20in%20the%20State%20List.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-industrial-liquor-verdict-in-landmark-verdict-top-court-says-states-can-rule-on-industrial-liquor-6853367%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl