g-over%2Farticleshow%2F114492100.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rise%20Of%20Marriage%20Apps%20In%20Pak%2C%20Claiming%20To%20Be%20'Halal'%2C%20With%20Chaperone%20Options%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20traditional%20matchmakers%20play%20a%20revered%20role%20in%20moulding%20daughters%20into%20potential%20brides%2C%20but%20marriage%20apps%20marketing%20themselves%20as%20halal%20are%20offering%20women%20a%20new%20route%20to%20finding%20a%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20saw%20my%20colleague%20happy%20after%20being%20married%20to%20someone%20she%20met%20online...%20I%20thought%2C%20since%20we%20have%20tried%20rishta%20aunties%20for%20four%20or%20five%20years%2C%20let's%20try%20this%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Ezza%20Nawaz%2C%20a%20textile%20designer%20in%20Lahore%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishta%20aunties%20--%20or%20traditional%20matchmakers%20--%20polish%20up%20women%20and%20present%20them%20to%20the%20families%20of%20potential%20suitors%2C%20in%20a%20country%20where%20dating%20is%20considered%20dishonourable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20marriage%20apps%20for%20Muslims%20have%20emerged%20in%20Pakistan%20promising%20so-called%20%26quot%3Blove%20matches%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20offer%20a%20%26quot%3Bchaperone%26quot%3B%20option%20--%20which%20provides%20a%20weekly%20transcript%20of%20sent%20and%20received%20messages%20to%20a%20chosen%20relative%2C%20satisfying%20families%20wary%20of%20their%20son%20or%20daughter%20connecting%20with%20strangers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Ezza%2C%20it%20was%20a%20success%3A%20just%20three%20months%20after%20meeting%20Waseem%20Akhtar%20on%20Muzz%2C%20she%20was%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20went%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20dates%20before%20we%20got%20our%20family%20involved.%20We%20took%20our%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2080%20percent%20of%20Pakistanis%20have%20arranged%20marriages%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20by%20Gallup%20and%20Gilani%20Pakistan%2C%20where%20families%20decide%20the%20union%2C%20sometimes%20settling%20an%20engagement%20without%20the%20bride%20and%20the%20groom%20even%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParents%20enlist%20the%20help%20of%20professional%20rishta%20aunties%20to%20help%20find%20a%20suitable%20family%2C%20with%20the%20first%20impression%20often%20based%20on%20how%20the%20young%20woman%20looks%20as%20she%20pours%20tea%20for%20her%20potential%20in-laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20app%2C%20however%2C%20says%201.2%20million%20Pakistanis%20have%20signed%20up%20since%20it%20launched%20last%20year%20with%20an%20advertising%20campaign%20in%20major%20cities%2C%20and%2015%2C000%20people%20have%20already%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarriage%20apps%20describe%20themselves%20as%20%26quot%3Bhalal%26quot%3B%2C%20or%20permissible%20in%20Islam%2C%20offering%20options%20to%20blur%20profile%20pictures%20for%20privacy%20and%20making%20clear%20the%20purpose%20is%20to%20reach%20a%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20continue%20to%20battle%20a%20stigma%20linking%20them%20to%20casual%20dating%20apps%20such%20as%20Tinder%2C%20which%20has%20been%20banned%20in%20Pakistan%20for%20being%20%26quot%3Bimmoral%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20tell%20people%20how%20I%20met%20my%20wife%20until%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20the%20person%20would%20not%20judge%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Waseem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETradition%20dates%20modernity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarriage%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20coming%20together%20of%20two%20families%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20where%20many%20live%20in%20multigenerational%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoosing%20your%20husband%20or%20wife%20yourself%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20deeply%20ingrained%20reverence%20towards%20elders%20and%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20traditional%20family%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishta%20aunties%20are%20therefore%20relied%20upon%20to%20find%20suitors%20from%20acceptable%20families%20--%20a%20process%20that%20young%20women%2C%20who%20are%20widely%20expected%20to%20marry%20by%20the%20age%20of%2025%2C%20can%20sometimes%20find%20demeaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20asked%20not%20to%20tell%20the%20guy's%20family%20that%20my%20hobbies%20are%20hiking%20or%20photography%2C%20but%20are%20cooking%20and%20cleaning...%20it%20made%20me%20angry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rida%20Fatima.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20the%20audacity%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20I%20looked%2C%20what%20I%20did%2C%20how%20much%20I%20earned%2C%20who%20my%20family%20is%2C%20how%20many%20brothers%20I%20have%2C%20what%20are%20my%20future%20aspirations.%20So%20every%20little%20thing%20is%20judged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFatima%20was%20presented%20with%20several%20potential%20matches%20through%20a%20rishta%20auntie%20appointed%20by%20her%20parents%2C%20but%20was%20asked%20to%20pay%20around%20%24700%20for%20an%20introductory%20meeting%20with%20a%20guy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rate%20fluctuates%20depending%20on%20whether%20the%20match%20has%20a%20foreign%20passport%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20she%20ditched%20the%20process%2C%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%2018%20percent%20of%20Pakistanis%20who%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Blove%20marriage%26quot%3B%20after%20meeting%20her%20husband%20by%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20how%20the%20guy%20looks%2C%20even%20if%20he%20is%20bald%20or%20has%20a%20big%20belly%2C%20he%20wants%20a%20wife%20who%20looks%20like%20a%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Muskan%20Ali%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20at%20a%20marriage%20consultancy%20in%20Karachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWaste%20of%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishta%20aunties%20do%20not%20feel%20threatened%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20offices%20buzz%20with%20parents%20and%20their%20children%20crafting%20profiles%20on%20computers%2C%20as%20matchmakers%20strive%20to%20digitise%20their%20businesses%20with%20sleek%20websites%20and%20WhatsApp%20groups%20for%20client%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsultants%20teach%20young%20women%20how%20to%20walk%2C%20talk%20and%20dress%20to%20best%20correspond%20to%20the%20wishes%20of%20their%20future%20in-laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20traditional%20matchmakers%20like%20Fauzia%20Aazam%2C%20the%20head%20of%20a%20community%20of%20rishta%20aunties%20in%20Rawalpindi%2C%20reject%20marriage%20apps%20altogether.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20waste%20time%20on%20these%20apps%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChatting%20together%20all%20through%20the%20night%2C%20I%20just%20don't%20like%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Fauzia%20Aazam%20(C)%2C%20the%20head%20of%20a%20community%20of%20rishta%20aunties%2C%20with%20other%20matchmakers%20during%20an%20annual%20meeting%20in%20Rawalpindi%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Fauzia%20Aazam%20(C)%2C%20the%20head%20of%20a%20community%20of%20rishta%20aunties%2C%20with%20other%20matchmakers%20during%20an%20annual%20meeting%20in%20Rawalpindi%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F8on79mlo_pak-dating-apps_625x300_23_October_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFauzia%20Aazam%20(C)%2C%20the%20head%20of%20a%20community%20of%20rishta%20aunties%2C%20with%20other%20matchmakers%20during%20an%20annual%20meeting%20in%20Rawalpindi%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20AFP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Aisha%20Sarwari%2C%20a%20feminist%20author%2C%20the%20matchmaking%20process%20is%20about%20exercising%20%26quot%3Bcontrol%26quot%3B%20over%20daughters-in-law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20that%20we%20need%20to%20find%20a%20good%20middle%20ground%2C%20where%20the%20respect%20is%20equal%20on%20both%20sides%20and%20there%20is%20no%2