8%20and%202013.%20With%20three%20children%20to%20raise%2C%20this%20initiative%20created%20a%20significant%20financial%20burden.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20the%20additional%20strain%20raised%20concerns%20in%20the%20household%2C%20his%20son%20Khangembam%20Chinglensana%20Singh%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20a%20bakery%20had%20opened%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20My%20mother%20decided%20to%20sell%20bakery%20items%20in%20Kumbi%20and%20neighbouring%20villages%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chinglensana%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20some%20concerns%2C%20but%20we%20all%20knew%20that%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20dream%20was%20a%20righteous%20one.%20We%20continue%20to%20contribute%20in%20whatever%20way%20we%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Indrakumar%2C%20too%2C%20helps%20sell%20the%20bakery%20items%20after%20school%20hours.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20even%20sold%20a%20portion%20of%20his%20own%20land%20to%20ensure%20there%20was%20no%20fund%20shortage.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndrakumar%20was%20never%20confined%20to%20the%20classroom.%20When%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20imparting%20lessons%2C%20he%20taught%20students%20the%20importance%20of%20humility%2C%20cleanliness%2C%20and%20hygiene%20through%20his%20actions.%20From%20carrying%20water%20on%20his%20bicycle%20for%20the%20students%20to%20cleaning%20the%20school%2C%20Indrakumar%20wants%20to%20instil%20in%20them%20that%20no%20work%20is%20too%20small.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-27-at-8.32.55-PM_11zon-1729604240.jpeg%3Fresize%3D1997%252C900%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221997%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khagembam%20Indrakumar%20Singh%20interacts%20with%20his%20students%20during%20one%20of%20his%20Sunday%20Campaigns.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F20