y-chad-stahelski-david-leitch-interview-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20celebrating%20the%20movie's%2010th%20anniversary%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20financing%20independently%20to%20get%20the%20bond%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20investors%20couldn't%20raise%20the%20money%20in%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20that%20point%2C%20Stahelski%2C%20Leitch%2C%20and%20Reeves%20had%20put%20their%20own%20money%20into%20the%20movie%20%E2%80%94%20the%20producer%20Basil%20Iwanyk%20had%20even%20maxed%20out%20three%20credit%20cards.%20It%20seemed%20as%20if%20%26quot%3BJohn%20Wick%26quot%3B%20might%20never%20see%20the%20light%20of%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20someone%20threw%20a%20Hail%20Mary.%20CAA%2C%20which%20was%20putting%20the%20financing%20together%2C%20offered%20some%20of%20its%20actors%20who%20had%20bankroll%20the%20opportunity%20to%20invest%2C%20Leitch%20explained%20to%20BI.%20It%20promised%20they'd%20be%20the%20first%20to%20get%20paid%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223532%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eva%20Longoria%20being%20photographed%20on%20the%20red%20carpet%2C%20wearing%20a%20shiny%20silver%20dress.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67178afca0a0cc14f222e6e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222649%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEva%20Longoria.%3Cp%3EPascal%20Le%20Segretain%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEva%20Longoria%20answered%20the%20call%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BJohn%20Wick%26quot%3B%20became%20her%20first%20major%20producer%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20becoming%20a%20household%20name%20on%20the%20hit%202000s%20TV%20series%20%26quot%3BDesperate%20Housewives%2C%26quot%3B%20Longoria%20has%20become%20a%20producing%20power%20player%20with%20her%20production%20company%2C%20UnbeliEVAble%20Entertainment%2C%20which%20she%20founded%20in%202005%20(it%20was%20acquired%20in%202023%20by%20Hyphenate%20Media%20Group%2C%20which%20Longoria%20cofounded).%20She's%20since%20produced%20the%20Lifetime%20series%20%26quot%3BDevious%20Maids%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20ran%20from%202013%20to%202016%3B%20the%202015%20NBC%20series%20%26quot%3BTelenovela%26quot%3B%3B%20and%20the%202019%20ABC%20series%20%26quot%3BGrand%20Hotel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20came%20to%20the%20rescue%2C%20and%20she%20provided%20the%20gap%20financing%2C%20literally%20less%20than%2024%20hours%20before%20we%20had%20to%20lock%20the%20doors%20on%20the%20movie%20and%20walk%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Stahelski%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20producer%20Iwanyk%20never%20disclosed%20who%20came%20through%20with%20the%20money%20until%20after%20%26quot%3BJohn%20Wick%26quot%3B%20became%20a%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasil%20took%20us%20out%20to%20dinner%2C%20and%20we%20were%20laughing%20about%20all%20the%20bullshit%20that%20happened%2C%20and%20he%20said%3A%20'By%20the%20way%2C%20funny%20story%2C%20you%20know%20who%20gap%20financed%20you%3F%20Eva%20Longoria.'%20We%20were%20like%2C%20'What!'%26quot%3B%20Stahelski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chad%20Stahelski%2C%20David%20Leitch%20and%20Keanu%20Reeves%20in%20black%20suits%20standing%20next%20to%20each%20other%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62d7ec5cf7ae6500183435a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221993%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChad%20Stahelski%2C%20David%20Leitch%2C%20and%20Reeves%20at%20the%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BJohn%20Wick%26quot%3B%20in%202014.%3Cp%3EJamie%20McCarthy%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStahelski%20and%20Leitch%20had%20never%20met%20Longoria%2C%20so%20they%20took%20her%20to%20lunch%20at%20the%20Chateau%20Marmont.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20laughing%2C%20going%2C%20'I%20didn't%20think%20it%20was%20going%20to%20work%2C'%26quot%3B%20Stahelski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Leitch%20ran%20into%20Longoria%20last%20year%20at%20an%20event%2C%20they%20couldn't%20help%20talking%20about%20%26quot%3BJohn%20Wick.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20reminiscing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20like%2C%20'Wow%2C%20that%20was%20the%20best%20money%20I've%20ever%20spent.'%20It%20paid%20back%20significantly%20for%20her.%26quot%3B%20(%26quot%3BJohn%20Wick%26quot%3B%20went%20on%20to%20earn%20more%20than%20%2486%20million%20worldwide%20on%20a%20%2420%20million%20budget.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20has%20this%20opened%20the%20door%20for%20Longoria%20to%20go%20on%20screen%20in%20an%20action%20movie%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20wants%20to%20for%20sure%2C%20she%20wants%20to%20do%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Leitch%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20love%20to%20work%20with%20her%2C%20we're%20trying%20to%20find%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feva-longoria-producer-john-wick-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729629688000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67178a659b3250dbbce91409%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feva-longoria-producer-john-wick-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BJohn%20Wick%26quot%3B%20directors%20explain%20how%20Eva%20Longoria%20became%20the%20unlikely%20savior%20of%20the%20movie%20when%20it%20ran%20out%20of%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jguerrasio%40insider.com%20(Jason%20Guerrasio)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A862%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feva-longoria-producer-john-wick-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20I%20got%20my%20first%20credit%20card%2C%20my%20dad%20gave%20me%203%20pieces%20of%20advice.%2020%20years%20later%2C%20I%20still%20follow%20them.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20t