3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-starter-credit-cards%5C%22%3Efirst%20credit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Once%20I%20had%20the%20card%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20solid%20credit%20limit%20%E2%80%94%20in%20hand%2C%20I%20envisioned%20how%20I%20would%20use%20that%20card%20to%20finish%20furnishing%20my%20new%20condo%2C%20buy%20airline%20tickets%2C%20or%20cover%20Sunday%20brunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20casually%20having%20a%20conversation%20with%20my%20dad%20and%20I%20mentioned%20that%20I%20got%20a%20credit%20card.%20His%20response%20was%20less%20than%20thrilled.%20%26quot%3BA%20credit%20card%3F%20That%20is%20the%20quickest%20road%20to%20debt!%20You%20have%20to%20handle%20a%20credit%20card%20responsibly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECredit%20card%20debt%20reached%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorkfed.org%2Fnewsevents%2Fnews%2Fresearch%2F2023%2F20230808%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%20%241%20trillion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Federal%20Reserve.%20So%20he%20wasn't%20wrong%3A%20Americans%20are%20carrying%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20credit%20card%20debt%20ever%20and%20paying%20the%20high%20interest%20rate%20charges%20that%20come%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20conversation%20with%20my%20dad%20on%20how%20to%20responsibly%20use%20a%20credit%20card%2C%20here%20are%20three%20pieces%20of%20advice%20that%20I%20still%20use%20to%20this%20day%2C%2020%20years%20later%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Start%20with%20manageable%20charges%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20immediately%20charging%20that%20%242%2C000%20dining%20room%20table%2C%20make%20reasonable%20charges%20that%20you%20can%20pay%20off%20quickly%20and%20won't%20put%20you%20into%20debt.%20When%20you%20use%20a%20credit%20card%20to%20purchase%20an%20item%20you%20really%20can't%20afford%2C%20you%20end%20up%20carrying%20that%20ba