0Working%20in%20the%20fields%2C%20we%20are%20living%20a%20luxurious%20lifestyle%20in%20our%20village%2C%20with%20city%20amenities%20nearby%20and%20pollution%20far%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Sarla%20Mann%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC9916933%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoringa%20oleifera%3A%20An%20Updated%20Comprehensive%20Review%20of%20Its%20Pharmacological%20Activities%2C%20Ethnomedicinal%2C%20Phytopharmaceutical%20Formulation%2C%20Clinical%2C%20Phytochemical%2C%20and%20Toxicological%20Aspects%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20in%20PubMed%20Central%20(PMC)%20in%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729608103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D371313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20working%20for%2011%20years%20at%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20(TCS)%2C%20Jitender%20Mann%20moved%20back%20to%20his%20ancestral%20home%20in%20Haryana%20to%20embrace%20organic%20farming.%20Along%20with%20his%20wife%20Sarla%2C%20he%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20to%20promote%20the%20goodness%20of%20moringa%20and%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20out%20of%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F371313%2Fcouple-quit-city-life-to-move-to-haryana-village-earns-lakhs-with-moringa-farming%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Abercrombie%20%26amp%3B%20Fitch%20CEO%20arrested%20for%20'sex-trafficking%