3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362788%2Fcurious-parent-harpreet-singh-grover-indian-parenting-tips-instagram-new-mom-parents-toddlers-select-schools-growth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20keeping%20their%20babies%20engaged%2C%20particularly%20as%20they%20begin%20to%20walk.%20It%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20important%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20entertain%20and%20educate%20children%20while%20minimising%20screen%20exposure%2C%20and%20many%20parents%20in%20parenting%20groups%20have%20a%20common%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20we%20keep%20our%20children%20screen-free%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Haripriya%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20had%20the%20same%20query%20when%20her%20second%20child%20was%20born%20in%202017.%20She%20searched%20for%20open-ended%20toys%20that%20would%20both%20educate%20and%20entertain.%20In%20her%20quest%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20she%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20alone%20in%20struggling%20to%20find%20suitable%20options.%20To%20provide%20her%20then%20two-year-old%20and%20three-month-old%20with%20toys%20that%20would%20help%20them%20learn%20life%20skills%2C%20she%20founded%20Extrokids%2C%20a%20business%20%E2%80%9Cdedicated%20to%20catering%20extraordinary%20kids%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20a%20business%20while%20caring%20for%20a%20three-month-old%20and%20a%20toddler%20was%20no%20easy%20feat%20for%20the%2034-year-old.%20Every%20step%20presented%20challenges%2C%20especially%20with%20naysayers%20in%20her%20family%20who%20believed%20she%20should%20focus%20solely%20on%20raising%20her%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20achieve%20her%20goal%20of%20providing%20parents%20with%20essential%20resources%20for%20their%20child%E2%80%99s%20development%2C%20she%20persevered.%20She%20found%20support%20in%20her%20mother%2C%20who%20joined%20her%20a%20few%20years%20later%20and%20is%20now%20the%20face%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20was%20rocky%2C%20but%20Haripriya%20emphasises%20consistency%20is%20key.%20She%20kept%20at%20it%2C%20whether%20it%20meant%20waiting%20for%20a%20month%20for%20her%20first%20order%2C%20enduring%20losses%2C%20or%20struggling%20to%20pay%20salaries.%20Her%20patience%20and%20perseverance%20were%20rewarded%3B%20today%2C%20Extrokids%20receives%20over%2015%2C000%20orders%20per%20month%2C%20boasts%20a%20catalogue%20of%20over%20500%20toys%2C%20has%20nearly%20five%20lakh%20followers%20on%20Instagram%2C%20and%20has%20served%20over%20five%20lakh%20customers%20to%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaripriya%20had%20started%20the%20venture%20with%20just%20Rs%205%2C000%20from%20her%20house%20in%20Coimbatore%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20Challenges%3A%20Haripriya%E2%80%99s%20Path%20to%20Success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9CManchester%20of%20South%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20BSc%20electronics%20graduate%20tried%20her%20hand%20at%20different%20businesses%20before%20the%20birth%20of%20her%20second%20child%2C%20including%20selling%20gifts%2C%20eco-friendly%20napkins%2C%20and%20offering%20tutorial%20lessons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20postpartum%20period%20affects%20every%20new%20mother%20differently%2C%20and%20for%20Haripriya%2C%20it%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20strong%20desire%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20particularly%20for%20parents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-16-at-11.43.09-2-min-1729061169-500x883.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Banu%20with%20some%20toys%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%